# Frontend Quality

- Use semantic markup.
- Avoid duplicated UI logic.
- Protect JS against missing DOM nodes.
- Avoid duplicate initializations.
- Keep selectors stable.
- Handle mobile layout.
- Add clear empty/loading/error states.
- Preserve existing backend field contracts.
